                'title' => 'STRESSSENSE: A STRESS LEVEL DETECTOR FOR DETERMINATION OF STRESS LEVEL THROUGH THE COMBINATION OF PHYSIOLOGICAL DATA OF GALVANIC SKIN RESPONSE AND PULSE RATE',
